NK039(ti)001:1: // 'phags pa rdo rje nag mo dbang phyug ma zhes bya ba'i sngags rgyud kyi rgyal po bzhugs so //
NK039(ti)001:3: +aar+ya badz+ra di b+ai k+aa l+ai shwa r+ai n+aa ma man+t+ra tan+t+ra r+aa dza /
NK039(ti)001:5: 'phags pa rdo rje nag mo dbang phyug ma zhes bya ba'i sngags rgyud kyi rgyal po /
NK039(ti)001:6: bcom ldan 'das mngon rdzogs kyi rgyal po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK039(ti)001:7: 'di skad bdag gis thos pa'i dus gcig na /

NK039(ti)001:12: thig le'i chos mthar thug pa'i ngang nas sprul pa /
NK039(ti)001:13: snang srid kyi bdag mo chen mo snod bcud la dbang sgyur ba 'byung ba'i rgyal po lnga dang /

NK039(ti)001:18: gsang ba'i bdag po phyag na rdo rje dang thabs
NK039(ti)001:19: cig go // srid pa gsum gyi gnod sbyin ma'i tshogs gdug pa'i mtshon cha dang po dang /

NK039(ti)001:22: mi'i sha khrag dang srog dbugs la sogs pa la dbang byed pa /
NK039(ti)001:23: 'jig rten du bskal pa ma yin bskal pa dang /

NK039(ti)001:33: khrag dang zhag gi dri snom pa /
NK039(ti)001:34: sems can thams cad la rnam par 'tshe ba /
NK039(ti)001:35: nang gi rgyan bab na gcig la gcig gi rigs khyod dang /
NK039(ti)001:36: bu la sogs pa za bar byed pa /
NK039(ti)001:37: nyungs bdun 'cha' zhing smug rtsi skud pa dang /
NK039(ti)001:38: shin tu sgeg pa'i tshogs rnams la /

NK039(ti)001:42: pa'i srin mo chen mo dmod pa'i mtshon cha can

NK039(ti)001:46: bdag mo dmod pa'i mtshon cha can dang /

NK039(ti)001:48: bdud mo gnod sbyin spun gsum dmod pa'i mtshon cha can dang /

NK039(ti)001:53: khyab pa dang thabs cig tu bzhugs te /
NK039(ti)001:54: de'i tshe de dag gi nang nas /
NK039(ti)001:55: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po /
NK039(ti)001:56: gsang ba'i bdag po phyag na rdo rjes /
NK039(ti)001:57: bcom ldan 'das mngon rdzogs kyi rgyal po la 'di skad ces gsol to //
NK039(ti)001:58: zhing dang bskal pa 'di nyid la //

NK039(ti)001:61: sems can rnams la rnam par 'tshe //

NK039(ti)001:69: phyag rgya dbang bskur sbyor ba gnyis //

NK039(ti)001:75: don dam pa 'dri bar gyur to //
NK039(ti)001:76: srin mo chen mo'i rgyud ni /

NK039(ti)001:79: de nas bcom ldan 'das mngon rdzogs rgyal pos /

NK039(ti)001:81: nyi zla'i steng du gnas yul gyi khro mor gyur te /

NK039(ti)001:1433: gal te bka' bzhin mi byed na //
NK039(ti)001:1434: dkyil 'khor gru gsum sum brtsegs la //
NK039(ti)001:1435: ma mo de gsum shes pa gzir //
NK039(ti)001:1436: dur khrod ro ras 'khar sil la //
NK039(ti)001:1437: ma yi mtha' mar rang snying bri //
NK039(ti)001:1438: lus du seng ldeng lcags skyer phur //
NK039(ti)001:1439: byang shar gtor ma sprin khengs can //
NK039(ti)001:1440: lho ru brub khung tsher mas dgang //
NK039(ti)001:1441: k+ai la ya'am che mchog gi //
NK039(ti)001:1442: nga rgyal bskyed de thugs kar phata //
NK039(ti)001:1443: grangs med h+aum gis mtha' ma bskor //
NK039(ti)001:1444: bsnyen bris phur bu g.yon bzung la //
NK039(ti)001:1445: sha ser gzir ba'i sngags 'bum bzlas //
NK039(ti)001:1446: ma ma trig nan re ma ti //
NK039(ti)001:1447: ta la mes spras de la i //
NK039(ti)001:1448: o i gnyis kyis brgyan par bya //
NK039(ti)001:1450: i ste ha la mes mtshan bya //
NK039(ti)001:1451: kha mun tra bam rak+sha dun //
NK039(ti)001:1452: dun dza tri ste u'i 'og legs //
NK039(ti)001:1453: ta la me ste u u dbang //
NK039(ti)001:1454: yi ge nyi shu rtsa bzhi ni //
NK039(ti)001:1455: ya mo gsum po gnad la bor //
NK039(ti)001:1456: 'bum phrag gcig gi bzlas pa byed //
NK039(ti)001:1457: h+aum phata nag po'i 'od zer gyis //
NK039(ti)001:1458: srid pa'i ma gsung dbang bsdus te //
NK039(ti)001:1459: mar thim nag mo ral pa can //
NK039(ti)001:1460: nyi ma'i go zu mdog dmar can //
NK039(ti)001:1461: khro bos dbu mnan mdangs bkrag phrog /
NK039(ti)001:1462: rak+sha ma ma sa ma ya //
NK039(ti)001:1463: s+t+wam zhes sa sna tas spras pa //
NK039(ti)001:1464: de la wa ldan a am ste //
NK039(ti)001:1465: trig nan sa ma ya stam zhes //
NK039(ti)001:1466: ta la mes te steng du bkra //
NK039(ti)001:1467: sa la te ste de la wa //
NK039(ti)001:1468: de steng o e ldan par bya //
NK039(ti)001:1469: yi ge bcu bzhi de dag ni //
NK039(ti)001:1470: phur btab bdud rtsi blud pa yin //
NK039(ti)001:1471: dza dza re ma ti dza zhes //
NK039(ti)001:1472: e i mdzes pa'i gong mi sgrags //
NK039(ti)001:1473: dbugs rgyun rtsa ni dza la dza la //
NK039(ti)001:1474: a dang rasna ga ya u //
NK039(ti)001:1475: ra yis sna la tsa yis spras //
NK039(ti)001:1476: rtsa rgyun de ni snying la b+h+yo //
NK039(ti)001:1477: rasna tsa ste ra la ga /
NK039(ti)001:1478: de la us spras sa sna nya //
NK039(ti)001:1479: de la i ste mtha' mar srog /
NK039(ti)001:1480: rak+mo ha ra hur dun b+h+yo //
NK039(ti)001:1481: o u a ste tha mar srog /
NK039(ti)001:1482: rag mo thun ni b+h+yo b+h+yo zhes //
NK039(ti)001:1483: o u i ste srog gnyis mtha' //
NK039(ti)001:1484: rtsa bdun sngags kyi phreng ba ste //
NK039(ti)001:1485: thob par 'phags pa'i las bya na //
NK039(ti)001:1487: 'phags pa rdo rje nag mo dbang phyug ma'i sngags
NK039(ti)001:1488: rgyud las shis bstan pa'i le'u ste bcu bzhi pa'o
NK039(ti)001:1489: //// de nas byang chub sems dpa' chen pos phyag
NK039(ti)001:1490: na rdo rje la sogs pa'i 'khor 'dus pa chen
NK039(ti)001:1491: //// pa'i tshogs kyis / bcom ldan 'das mngon rdzogs
NK039(ti)001:1492: kyi rgyal po dang ral pa gcig ma la bstod
NK039(ti)001:1493: //// pa'i tshogs kyis / pa / e ma ho ngo mtshar mngon rdzogs che //
NK039(ti)001:1494: e ma ho sangs rgyas kun gyi sku //
NK039(ti)001:1495: 'bar ba chen po'i gar dgu yis //
NK039(ti)001:1496: don byed rang bzhin khyod la 'dud //
NK039(ti)001:1497: e ma e ma ya mtshan che //
NK039(ti)001:1498: sgra ni ri rab 'bum bsnyil bzhin //
NK039(ti)001:1499: sems can thams cad dbang du sdug /
NK039(ti)001:1500: h+aum phata sgra chen khyod la 'dud //
NK039(ti)001:1501: e ma de bzhin gshegs pa'i thugs //
NK039(ti)001:1502: shin tu zad pa rgya mtsho'i gting //
NK039(ti)001:1503: nyon mongs thams cad sreg par byed //
NK039(ti)001:1504: mi rtog thugs chen khyod la 'dud //
NK039(ti)001:1505: e ma dpal ldan ral gcig ma //
NK039(ti)001:1506: ya mtshan chen mo dbu bcu bdun //
NK039(ti)001:1507: spyan ni lnga bcu gcig dang ldan //
NK039(ti)001:1508: phyag ni sum cu rtsa bzhi ste //
NK039(ti)001:1509: shin tu 'jigs pa'i phyag mtshan can //
NK039(ti)001:1510: srin mo'i tshogs rnams 'dul byed ma //
NK039(ti)001:1511: 'jig rten rnams ni bde la bkod //
NK039(ti)001:1514: byang chub sems dpa' phyag na rdo rje la sogs
NK039(ti)001:1515: pa'i 'khor thams cad rjes su yi rang bar gyur
NK039(ti)001:1516: to // 'phags pa rdo rje nag mo dbang phyug ma'i sngags rgyud las /
NK039(ti)001:1517: bstod cing rjes su yi rangs pa'i le'u ste bco lnga pa'o ////
